{"article_id":"vDUI294501ye6XMe","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The CIA believes","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman ordered the murder of journalist Jamal Khashoggi ,","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"according to US media reports .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Sources close to the agency said","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"it had assessed the evidence in detail .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"It is understood there is no `` smoking gun ''","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"but US officials think","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"such an operation would need the prince 's approval .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Saudi Arabia has called the claim false","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"and insisted","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that the crown prince knew nothing about plans for the killing .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"It says","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Khashoggi was killed","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"as a result of a `` rogue operation '' .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"US President Donald Trump has spoken to CIA Director Gina Haspel and Secretary of State Mike Pompeo about the CIA 's assessment of the Khashoggi murder ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"the White House says .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"Press secretary Sarah Sanders gave no details","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"but said","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Mr Trump had confidence in the CIA .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Before the briefing , President Trump stressed the importance of Saudi Arabia to the US ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"as he has done","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"since news of Khashoggi 's killing emerged .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"`` They have been a truly spectacular ally in terms of jobs and economic development , ''","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"`` I have to take a lot of things into consideration . ''","depth":4},{"id":25,"text":"While there has been widespread international condemnation of Khashoggi 's murder","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"there has been little in the way of substantial action .","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"The journalist was killed","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"after entering the Saudi consulate in Istanbul on 2 October","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"to obtain a marriage document .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"His body has not been found .","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"Turkey also insists","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"the order","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"to kill him","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"came from the highest levels .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"The Washington Post ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"which Khashoggi worked for ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"says","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"the CIA assessment was based partly on a phone call","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"made by the crown prince 's brother , Prince Khalid bin Salman , the Saudi ambassador to the US .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Prince Khalid allegedly called Khashoggi at the direction of his brother","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and gave him assurances","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that he would be safe to go to the consulate .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Prince Khalid , now back in Saudi Arabia , said on Twitter","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"that he had not been in contact with Khashoggi for nearly a year .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"he had never suggested Khashoggi","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"who had been in London for a conference until the day before his disappearance -","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"should go to Turkey for any reason .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"It is understood agents have also examined a call","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"made to a senior aide of Crown Prince bin Salman by the team","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that carried out the killing .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"Sources","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"quoted in the US media","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"stressed","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"that there was no single piece of evidence","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"linking the crown prince directly to the murder ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"but officials believe","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"such an operation would have needed his approval .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"At a news conference in Riyadh on Thursday , Deputy Public Prosecutor Shalaan bin Rajih Shalaan said","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"Khashoggi was given a lethal injection","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and his body was dismembered inside the consulate after his death .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"The body parts were then handed over to a local `` collaborator '' outside the grounds ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"he added .","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"A composite sketch of the collaborator has been produced","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and investigations are continuing to locate the remains .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Eleven unidentified people have been charged over the journalist 's death","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"and the prosecutor is seeking the death penalty for five of them .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"The reported CIA assessment","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"that MBS ordered the killing of Jamal Khashoggi","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"largely matches those in other Western capitals ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"including London .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"The purported intercepted phone call","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"- denied by the Saudis -","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"between MBS 's brother in Washington , Prince Khalid bin Salman , and Khashoggi ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"urging him to visit the Saudi consulate in Istanbul ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"would appear to be at the behest of the crown prince .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"A second intercepted phone call was from the hit team on the day of the murder to someone inside MBS 's inner circle in Riyadh .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Again , it is hard to believe","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"this would have been","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"without the Crown Prince 's knowledge","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"Taken together with the SIGINT","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"( signals intelligence ) ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"the case against MBS is damning but still circumstantial .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Government officials do not believe","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"there is a metaphorical `` smoking gun ''","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that explicitly ties MBS to the murder .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"drawing on well-established diplomatic and intelligence contacts ,","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"they know","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"that in that part of the world nothing gets done","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"without sign-off from the top .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"In the tightly controlled Arab Gulf states there is simply no such thing as `` a rogue operation , ''","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"as Saudi statements have described it .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"Meanwhile the glaring inconsistencies in the official Saudi explanations have only deepened suspicions of a state-sponsored cover-up .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":191,"left":120,"right":190,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":109,"right":119,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":109,"left":103,"right":108,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":103,"left":100,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":98,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":97,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":5,"right":101,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":101,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":108,"left":105,"right":107,"relation":"el